-- China Will Accelerate Personal Income Tax Overhaul, Politburo’s Wu Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-03-09T07:54:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-09/china-will-accelerate-personal-income-tax-overhaul-politburo-s-wu-says.html
China  will accelerate overhauling
the country’s personal income tax system to adjust the
distribution of income,  Wu Bangguo , head of China’s National
People’s Congress, said in a speech today in Beijing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
